"```diff\n"
"+void update_internal_node_key(void* node, uint32_t old_key, uint32_t new_key) {\n"
"+  uint32_t old_child_index = internal_node_find_child(node, old_key);\n"
"+  *internal_node_key(node, old_child_index) = new_key;\n"
" }\n"
"```"
